    <title>Implementing the Exponential Mechanism with Base-2 Differential Privacy</title>
    <link href="https://aurora2hl.github.io/post/b63ba420.html"/>
    <id>https://aurora2hl.github.io/post/b63ba420.html</id>
    <published>2022-07-18T02:28:39.000Z</published>
